msgid "Units unlock permanently"
msgstr "Desbloqueo de unidades permanente"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/name"
msgid "Falaise Pocket [SKIRMISH]"
msgstr "La Bolsa de Falaise [ESCARAMUZA]"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/name_big"
msgid "Falaise Pocket"
msgstr "La Bolsa de Falaise"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/story"
msgid "The Third Army advance from the south made good progress - Close the pocket.\n\nSoldiers of the 3rd Armored Division! You have a historical opportunity ahead. We can close the pocket around the main German force!\n\nGoals:\n - Advance North to close the pocket.\n - Annihilate the enemy."
msgstr ""
"El avance del Tercer Ejército desde el sur hizo buenos progresos# Cerrar la "
"bolsa.\n"
"\n"
"¡Soldados de la 3ª División Blindada!\n"
"\n"
"Tienen una oportunidad histórica por delante.\n"
"\n"
"¡Podemos cerrar el cerco alrededor de la principal fuerza alemana!\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"Objetivos:\n"
"\n"
" - Avanzar hacia el Norte para cerrar el cerco.\n"
"\n"
" - Aniquilar al enemigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/place"
msgid "Falaise, Calvados"
msgstr "Falaise, Calvados"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/date"
msgid "17 August, 1944"
msgstr "17 de agosto, 1944"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/outro_start"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Well done! This will go down in history as one of those really important "
"victories. You did very well."
msgstr ""
"¡Enhorabuena! Esto pasará a la historia como una de esas victorias realmente "
"importantes. Lo has hecho muy bien."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/outro_failed"
msgid "Well that failed. We can't let this happen, go back and try again!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, hemos fallado. No podemos dejar que esto vuelva a ocurrir, ¡da la "
"vuelta e inténtalo de nuevo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/outro_failed_hq"
msgid "We lost our HQ. That spells the end."
msgstr "Hemos perdido el cuartel general. Esto es el final."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/mission_hq"
msgid "You must hold your field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Debes defender tu cuartel general!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/mission_attack"
msgid "Punch a hole in the enemy position and drive north!"
msgstr "¡Ábrete camino entre las posiciones enemigas y avanza hacia el norte!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/flag_capture_status"
msgid "Your soldiers secured %1%/7 German positions!"
msgstr "¡Tus soldados aseguraron %1%/7 posiciones alemanas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/narrator_start0"
msgid ""
"Welcome back to the front line, Lieutenant! This is your field HQ, make sure "
"to keep it under your control!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido de nuevo al frente, Teniente! Este es tu cuartel general en "
"campo, ¡asegúrate de mantenerlo bajo nuestro control!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/narrator_start1"
msgid ""
"Gentlemen, there is no choice but to attack immediately. Orders from HQ were "
"quite clear, we can't afford to postpone the attack!"
msgstr ""
"Señores, no tenemos elección, hay que atacar inmediatamente. Las órdenes del "
"Cuartel General fueron muy claras, ¡no podemos permitirnos posponer el "
"ataque!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/narrator_start2"
msgid ""
"The germans will not expect us to attack from this direction, hopefully. "
"Let's get them!"
msgstr ""
"Los alemanes no esperarán que ataquemos desde esta dirección. ¡A por ellos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/narrator_start3"
msgid ""
"Begin the attack, meanwhile more reinforcements are being prepared for you!"
msgstr "Comienza el ataque, ¡mientras tanto se te harán llegar más refuerzos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Attention, Germans are approaching our Field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Atención, los alemanes se acercan a nuestro cuartel general!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/allied_enemy_plane"
msgid "Enemy plane!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡Avión enemigo!!!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/allied_enemy_plane2"
msgid "German aircraft inbound!"
msgstr "¡Aviones alemanes entrando!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid ""
"We must hold the command post at all costs! There is no room for retreat!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos mantener el puesto de mando a toda costa! ¡No hay lugar para la "
"retirada!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_skirmish_falaise_pocket/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request an airstrike."
msgstr "¡Mayor! Ahora puede solicitar un ataque aéreo."
